et.  I just had a few Q's for those who can answer. ^_^<br>
<br>
I don't spend time in Kunark, I'm not a Kunark kind of chick, really, I prefer to play in Sol B, where I know the people, and I know I can't get lost <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  .<br>
<br>
